{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "e3f018f4-41b3-4446-8c00-dfbab59fb18d", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e3f018f4-41b3-4446-8c00-dfbab59fb18d@3.pkg/1772597528466/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597529315", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e3f018f4-41b3-4446-8c00-dfbab59fb18d@3.pkg/1772597528466/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597529315"}, "identifier": "e3f018f4-41b3-4446-8c00-dfbab59fb18d", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>我国的分配方式包括按劳分配，按个体劳动者的劳动成果分配，按资本、技术、信息、管理、土地、劳动等生产要素分配。分析可知，王某3000元工资收入、12000元奖金收入属于按劳分配，①②符合题意；10000元炒股、8000元房租收入属于按生产要素分配，③④排除。故选B。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下表为国有企业职工王某2024年下半年的收入情况：</p>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:500px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>工资收入</td>\n\t\t\t<td>奖金收入</td>\n\t\t\t<td>炒股收入</td>\n\t\t\t<td>房租收入</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>30000元</td>\n\t\t\t<td>12000元</td>\n\t\t\t<td>10000元</td>\n\t\t\t<td>8000元</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>王某的收入方式中属于按劳分配的有（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①30000元工资收入 ②12000元奖金收入</p>\n\n<p>③10000元炒股收入 ④8000元房租收入</p>\n", "title": "下表为国有企业职工王某2024年下半年的收入情况：工资收入奖金收入炒股收入房租收入30000元12000元10000元8000元王某的收入方式中属于按劳分配的有（   ）①30000元工资收入 ②12000元奖金收入③10000元炒股收入 ④8000元房租收入", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "locat